{"id":"classify-imgs-2","label":"Classify the Images","pdf":"","lockAfter":2,"list":[{"label":"Healthy vs Unhealthy Foods","type":"group","id":"healthy-unhealthy","lockAfter":1,"onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below foods as healthy and unhealthy. Drag and drop or click and connect.","imageType":"custom","types":["Healthy","Unhealthy"]},"data":[["almond, carrot, apple, mushroom, cucumber,spinach","ice-cream, lollipop, cake, chocolate"],["salad, juice, cashewnut, corn, beetroot, banana","pizza, burger, soft-drink, french-fry"]]},{"label":"Domestic vs Wild Animals","type":"group","id":"domestic-wild","lockAfter":1,"onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below foods as healthy and unhealthy. Drag and drop or click and connect.","imageType":"custom","types":["Domestic Animals","Wild Animals"]},"data":[["cat, dog, goat, horse, pig","elephant, lion, monkey, rhino, tiger, zebra"],["cow, sheep, buffalo, donkey, camel","giraffe, hippo, bear, cheetah, hyena, antelope"]]},{"label":"Nature vs Man made","type":"group","id":"nature-human","onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below images as Natural or created by us. Drag and drop or click and connect. ","imageType":"custom","types":["Nature","Man Made"]},"data":[["tree, rainbow, waterfall, nest, grass","table, mat, mug, lock, fan"],["stone, pebbles, cloud, morning, night","chair, ball, clock, aeroplane, umbrella"],["sun, moon, bird, leaf, shell","dustbin, backpack, pillow, teddy, boat"]]},{"label":"Animals vs Birds","type":"group","id":"animals-birds","onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below images as Animals and Birds. Drag and drop or click and connect. ","imageType":"custom","types":["Animals","Birds"]},"data":[["goat, donkey, horse, elephant, lion","crow, hen, parrot, peacock, penguin"],["cheetah, giraffe, kangaroo, bear, camel","sparrow, rooster, owl, ostrich, macaw"]]},{"label":"Fruits vs Vegetables","type":"group","id":"fruits-vegs","onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below images as Fruits and Vegetables. Drag and drop or click and connect. ","imageType":"custom","types":["Fruits","Vegetables"]},"data":[["guava, apple, grapes, pineapple, pomegranate","carrot, onion, potato, cabbage, brinjal"],["banana, papaya, mango, watermelon, jackfruit","capsicum, radish, elephant-yam, raw-banana, bottlegourd"]]},{"label":"Kitchen vs Study room","type":"group","id":"study-kitchen","onlyBigScreen":true,"commonData":{"title":"Classify the below images based on whether they are found in study room or kitchen. Drag and drop or click and connect. ","imageType":"custom","types":["Study Room","Kitchen"]},"data":[["globe, stapler, literature, schoolbag, writingpad","pan, grinder, anjarai-petti, fridge, oven"],["notebook, ruler, sharpener, book, ink","dosaikal, blender, stove, plate, tap"]]}]}